Hmm, this is rather ambiguous indeed. I'm going to repaint it as:

#define ESR_ELx_ERET_ISS_ERET		0x2
#define ESR_ELx_ERET_ISS_ERETA		0x1

which matches the ARM ARM wording as of DDI0487G.b.

